edu.ncsu.csc216.carrental.util

Interface SimpleQueue<E>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Queue

    public interface SimpleQueue<E>
    A simple collection designed for holding elements prior to processing. A Queue typically orders elements in a FIFO (First-In-First-Out) manner.
    Author:
    David Wright
